|-|Meaning=
Her life is but a certain rain.
<br>
Steel is her body, and rain is her namesake.
<br>
The passing rain as myriad tears of the sky.
<br>
Not even once her luck yielded, not even once she could reach the end.
<br>
The bearer lies here alone, awaiting the end of the unending rain.
<br>
Thus in times of rain and shine, the timely rain will be always be together (with you).
<br>
And let the (late) autumn rain herald the path with a blessed future.
